At Crafty Entertainment Ltd we are committed to protecting and preserving the privacy of our visitors. This policy explains:
Who we are and how to contact us;
What information we collect from you whilst you visit our website (www.craftyquiz.com);
What information we collect from you whilst you use our products or services;
How we use and protect this information;
How we use any personal information that you provide to us;
How we use cookies;
Please read this privacy policy carefully and in full and note that we update this policy from time to time, so please review it regularly.
